17
00:00:32,590 --> 00:00:33,750
And to top it off,

18
00:00:33,750 --> 00:00:36,230
she now speaks fluent English.

19
00:00:36,230 --> 00:00:37,280
Now you would think,

20
00:00:37,280 --> 00:00:38,340
this would be a proud moment

21
00:00:38,340 --> 00:00:40,660
for Chinese international students.

22
00:00:40,660 --> 00:00:41,660
One of their own,

23
00:00:41,660 --> 00:00:42,810
singled out for achievement

24
00:00:42,810 --> 00:00:45,010
at an American University.

25
00:00:45,010 --> 00:00:47,810
