50
00:01:48,289 --> 00:01:50,849
and also staying hungry and foolish.

51
00:01:50,849 --> 00:01:52,990
It was a pretty great speech.

52
00:01:52,990 --> 00:01:55,630
But back to Ms. Yang's speech.

53
00:01:55,630 --> 00:01:58,139
Here was her key point:

54
00:01:58,139 --> 00:02:06,419
Freedom is oxygen. Freedom is passion.

55
00:02:06,419 --> 00:02:08,060
And then Chinese internet users

56
00:02:08,060 --> 00:02:11,390
