57
00:02:11,390 --> 00:02:12,390
And believe me,

58
00:02:12,390 --> 00:02:14,989
those were the more polite comments.

59
00:02:14,989 --> 00:02:17,210
THEY WERE HARD TO FIND!

60
00:02:17,210 --> 00:02:19,720
The speech also went viral on Weibo,

61
