81
00:03:05,260 --> 00:03:07,409
and are willing to make contributions for
her,

82
00:03:07,409 --> 00:03:09,329
I believe that the Chinese government

83
00:03:09,329 --> 00:03:12,189
will encourage, support and welcome it."

84
00:03:12,189 --> 00:03:14,620
You see, as long as you wholeheartedly love

85
00:03:14,620 --> 00:03:16,280
the Chinese Communist Party,

86
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:17,860
