the Communist party will encourage

88
00:03:19,250 --> 00:03:20,390
and welcome it.

89
00:03:20,390 --> 00:03:23,260
I think that was what he was saying?

90
00:03:23,260 --> 00:03:24,930
People always ask me

91
00:03:24,930 --> 00:03:30,290
